title: Cream Cheese Loaf Cake
ingredients: ["2 1/4 c. sifted flour", "1 tsp. baking powder", "1/4 tsp. salt", "1/2 c. shortening", "sugar", "2 eggs", "1 c. milk", "8 oz. cream cheese", "1 Tbsp. grated orange peel", "1/4 c. orange juice"]
directions: ["Sift together the flour, baking powder and salt.", "Cream the shortening and gradually add 1 1/2 cups of sugar, continuing to cream until light and fluffy.", "Beat in eggs, beating well.", "Add sifted dry ingredients, alternating with milk, beginning and ending with dry ingredients.", "Blend well after each addition.", "Cut cream cheese into 1/4-inch cubes and fold into batter along with orange peel.", "Turn batter into 2 greased and floured 9 x 5-inch loaf pans or 12 well-greased muffin tins.", "Bake at 375\u00b0 for 50 to 55 minutes for loaves or 20 to 25 minutes for muffins or until golden brown."]

title: Broccoli With Rice
ingredients: ["1 c. brown rice, cooked", "1 bunch fresh or frozen broccoli spears", "1 can mushroom soup", "1/2 c. soy mayonnaise", "1 tsp. McKay's chicken seasoning*", "1 tsp. turmeric", "1/4 c. slivered almonds"]
directions: ["Cool rice; spread in flat casserole dish.", "Parboil broccoli; arrange on top of rice.", "Combine mushrooms, mayonnaise and seasonings.", "(For thinner sauce, add 1 cup milk.)", "Top rice with sauce mixture.", "Sprinkle almonds on top.", "Bake 20 minutes at 350\u00b0 or until bubbly.", "Serve immediately."]
